item.title: CVE-2021-24233|2024-08-03T19:21:18.922Z -- unknown -- cooked%20ppro
item.description: The Cooked Pro WordPress plugin before 1.7.5.6 was affected by unauthenticated reflected Cross-Site Scripting issues, due to improper sanitisation of user input while being output back in pages as an arbitrary attribute.
